# Tests

Run with `bun test`. `bunfig.toml` preloads `test/preload.js` — sets `BUDGIE_DB` to a temp file (never touches `data/budgie.db`).

## DB tests

```js
import { useCleanDb, accountByName } from "./helpers.js";
useCleanDb(); // beforeEach → resetDatabase()
import { ... } from "../src/services/...";
```

- `resetDatabase()` wipes rows and re-seeds; for tests only.
- No full `Bun.serve` integration tests — call services, views, and `http.js` helpers directly.

## OFX fixtures

`ofxFile({ amount: -1234 })` uses **cents** → TRNAMT `-12.34`.

## Migration tests

`test/migrations.test.js` covers `runMigrations` and `user_version`. Add cases when new migrations have special upgrade logic.

Do not assume tests need new npm devDependencies.
